column5: 2 bedroom 2 bathroom duplex in a cul de sac in South Austin between S. 1st and S. congress. Very private and quiet from the other unit, just a shared driveway. Private patio is just for your side. 10-15 minutes to downtown. Walking distance to bars, Urban Winery, a rock climbing gym, and coffee shop among others. Construction going on next door.  Kitchen has all cookware needed. Cable TV. One car garage. 2 bikes!  Pets welcome but please clean up after them! Austin licensed
column8: Private home w/ outdoor space, 2 bikes, & cable TV
